# 📄 Product Requirement Document (PRD)

## Project Title: **Mecha Chameleon: Pig Protocol**
**Version:** 2.0.0  
**Status:** Architecture Revamp  
**Target:** Web Browsers (WebGL 2.0 / Socket.IO)

---

## 1. Product Overview & Core Loop
**Mecha Chameleon: Pig Protocol** is an asymmetric 3D multiplayer stealth hide-and-seek game. Players take on the role of low-poly pigs capable of morphing their skeletal postures, sticking to vertical walls, and painting their skin surfaces with an RGB eyedropper palette to blend into environmental textures. One designated **Hunter** wielding a shotgun must track down and eliminate all hidden pigs before time runs out.

---

## 2. User Roles & Matchmaking
1. **Runner Pig:** Must hide, paint, deform posture, and adhere to walls to avoid detection.
2. **Hunter:** Wields a shotgun, tracks disguised pigs, and eliminates them within a specified time limit.
3. **AI Bots:** Auto-fill engine supporting 10–20 AI-driven bot pigs for single-player / fill matches.

---

## 3. Game Lifecycle & Key Features

### 3.1 Main Menu
* **3D Viewport:** Center-rotating preview pig mesh.
* **Action Buttons:** `CREATE PARTY`, `JOIN PARTY`, and `PLAY VS BOTS (10-20 AI)`.

### 3.2 The Waiting Room (Pre-Game Lobby)
* **Physical Arena:** Enclosed 4-wall waiting room with a dynamic score-board wall and game logo wall.
* **Hunter Selection Tile:** A central elevated step. Players compete to stand on this tile before the lobby timer expires.
* **Selection Logic:** The player standing on the tile when time reaches zero becomes the Hunter. If contested or empty, a random player is selected.

### 3.3 Hiding Mechanics (Runners)
* **Body Resizing:** Slimmer, re-proportioned pig model (reduced box depth/width).
* **RGB Paint Brush System (C Key):** Replaces toggle camouflage. Opens an active HUD color picker and environment color eyedropper allowing players to paint body materials.
* **GTA-Style Pose Wheel (Tab Key):** Radial menu with 6 bone-deforming postures (Star Spread, Fetal Curl, Kneel Sit, Side Sleep, Stretch, Reset).
* **Wall Adhesion / Surface Stick:** Ability to latch onto vertical planes/walls to blend as wall props.

---

## 4. Victory Conditions
* **Hunter Win:** Eliminate all hidden pig players before the match timer expires.
* **Runners Win:** At least one pig survives until the match timer reaches 0:00.